<section
  class="section experience flex items-center justify-center"
  id="experience"
>
  <div class="bg-light-shadow rounded p-8 max-w-4xl w-full">
    <h2 class="section__title mb-4 translate" data-translate-key="experience">
      Experience
    </h2>

    <div class="experience-item mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
      <div>
        <img
          src="/municipalidadlogo.png"
          alt="Logo Municipalidad El Quisco"
          class="w-32 h-32 object-center object-cover mb-4"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h4 class="text-xl mb-2 text-primary">Municipalidad El Quisco</h4>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expmunicipalidadtitle"
        >
          Full Stack Developer
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expmunicipalidaddate"
        >
          October 2024 - Present
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expmunicipalidadabout"
        >
          Software Development, legacy software migration, and server management
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expmunicipalidaddesc"
        >
          I’ve developed multiple websites according to the company’s needs,
          migrated legacy software to more modern technologies, managed
          application servers, databases, and overseen various projects.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-2">
          Nextjs - Docker - SQL Server - TS - Tailwind CSS - HTML - Ubuntu
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-4 border-t border-divider white" />
    <br /><br />

    <div class="experience-item mb-4 flex items-center justify-center">
      <div>
        <img
          src="/duocuclogo.png"
          alt="Logo DUOC UC"
          class="w-32 h-32 object-center object-cover mb-4"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h4 class="text-xl mb-2 text-primary">DUOC UC</h4>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expduoctitle"
        >
          Professional Internship: Developer
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expduocdate"
        >
          September 2023 - December 2023
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expduocabout"
        >
          Development of a web management system for documents and resources.
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="expduocdesc"
        >
          The implementation of the web system brought the following benefits to
          the company: efficient task automation, remote access to information,
          centralization and organization of resources, data security, and
          improvement in data-driven decision-making.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-2">
          Django - Python - Tailwind CSS - JS - HTML
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-4 border-t border-divider white" />
    <br /><br />
    <div class="experience-item flex items-center justify-center">
      <div>
        <img
          src="/tvcostalogo.png"
          alt="Logo TV Costa"
          class="w-32 h-32 object-center object-cover mb-4"
          loading="lazy"
        />
        <h4 class="text-xl mb-2 text-primary">TV Costa</h4>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="exptvtitle"
        >
          Work Placement: Developer
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-2 translate" data-translate-key="exptvdate">
          February 2023 - March 2023
        </p>
        <p
          class="text-secondary mb-2 translate"
          data-translate-key="exptvabout"
        >
          Maintenance, error correction, and implementation of new
          functionalities for the company's website.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-2 translate" data-translate-key="exptvdesc">
          Website maintenance, error fixes, and enhancements yielded notable
          improvements for the company, ensuring a secure, efficient, and
          feature-rich online environment.
        </p>
        <p class="text-secondary mb-2">Wordpress - PHP</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .experience-item img {
    width: 33%;
